{"tid":1590334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[考古] 日本反華遊行叫囂中國侵略 將中國比作納粹","createTime":"2019-09-23T16:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T12:55:18.000Z","uid":267881,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e84ba04690d9e2e611219ab78d805d548cb23136","tid":1590334,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4k21F_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4k21F_d.jpg%3Fmaxwidth%3D640%26shape%3Dthumb%26fidelity%3Dmedium&h=dd9ee6c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/3976316/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F3976316%2F&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0objMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=017103be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/3976316/</a><br />\n<br />\n釣魚島嶼最新消息：近日，由於中日釣魚島時間的火熱升級，中國各地掀起反日遊行，中日關係空前白熱化，在此，日本民眾也舉起反中遊行，並肆意將中國稱為「chinazism」。<br />\r\n<br />\nChiNazism 這是一個合體詞由兩個單詞China和nazism構成，左邊一個是中國，右邊是德國納粹的意思，合起來之意是中國侵略的意思。對此，中國熱心網友們紛紛表示氣憤，對日本的非法行徑強烈抗議。有網友立即搶注 <a href=\"http://chinazism.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchinazism.com&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0objMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=479c45ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">chinazism.com</a> ，擔心被日本人註冊用於非法行為，並第一時間製作了簡單的網站，希望得到更多的國人在此抨擊心裡變態扭曲的日本人。"},{"pid":"86c3d14e1320a3077d041060b71cce3268157884","tid":1590334,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"f06bd88c701ead7d5e7374ba55bc7cf519eca442","tid":1590334,"uid":6980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}